{"tid":1885282,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(ps4)fifa pro club 2300-0300開波，搵有經驗隊友","createTime":"2020-02-18T07:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T08:09:26.000Z","uid":164652,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a42c3be3c7ae9e38489a59419631778bda1ebf45","tid":1885282,"uid":164652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"本身隊波 今年重組過，已有固定班底<br />\n隊波total 20個人到<br />\n但其實未必日日夠8個人而上開波<br />\n所以想搵多1,2個有經驗又可以輕鬆踢既隊友<br />\n<br />\n隊波踢開防反為主，閘位放直線落翼，再地波傳中到禁區<br />\n如果防反唔到，就短傳控球為主<br />\n踢開4231,切勿個人主義<br />\n<br />\n隊波keep主d1-d3上上落落視乎當日人腳<br />\n心態上，大家收工打下機，輕鬆下，但輕鬆之餘，希望大家都可以有少少進步，但千奇唔好屌友，大家打下機姐，同埋就算無mic,都（一定要入party）唔講野，都聽到我地講野<br />\n大家吹下水講下笑，無咁悶<br />\n<br />\n暫時想招 前場球員 st/翼/cam<br />\n最可以一個人打到幾個位，可以方便我掉配😅<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既加我psn <br />\nkit2222hk2000"},{"pid":"7a9dd368aba64ff3d48a190770fd972c19768245","tid":1885282,"uid":1629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"part time ok?"},{"pid":"84b2c2c2d2a74285a1aaca5c9ffccff0b1c2ce51","tid":1885282,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"隊名？"},{"pid":"f0148fc487c51f13bf2bf5029cf90451c8debe82","tid":1885282,"uid":58928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱加咗巴打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c776aa36837700e7742ace84d97eaa030f84593","tid":1885282,"uid":129766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"仲招唔招?"},{"pid":"57d95757fc12f572e8fdcee4cd095746fd2235a5","tid":1885282,"uid":164652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"暫時唔搵前場<br />\n搵閘同中堅<br />\n而加有時多過11個，打算分2隊"},{"pid":"6ac34ab75bf16ec75f07b931e71c7bd4346776d7","tid":1885282,"uid":164652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T20:10:39.000Z","msg":"推,招收閘位，同中堅<br />\nd1-d2 入party"},{"p